{"tid":167511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"撿窗外衣物 八旬婆婆10樓外牆半天吊","createTime":"2017-03-23T01:26:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T03:24:29.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f215bcff88da96c778ed3dc58911c6082033837b","tid":167511,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T01:26:49.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>撿窗外衣物 八旬婆婆10樓外牆半天吊<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170323/56466817\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170323%2F56466817&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=07e6790d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170323%2F56466817&h=c5007b7c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170323/56466817</a></strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n紅磡黃埔花園5期清樺苑發生驚險家居意外。清晨6時半左右，住在10樓的一名82歲老婆婆，因為有衣物跌在窗外冷氣機頂，於是拿竹支撩動嘗試撿拾，豈料失平衡自己也跌出窗外。千鈞一髮之際，她雙手捉住晾衫架半天吊。此時，在單位內的丈夫發現此狀，連忙捉住她的腳，由鄰居代為報警救起。消防員接報到場破門入屋，將婆婆救起，她沒有表面傷痕，但驚魂未定，送院檢驗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170323/large/1490228788_a5fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170323%2Flarge%2F1490228788_a5fe.jpg&h=b08de241&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n婆婆驚魂未定送院檢驗。(江寶龍攝)<br />\n<br />\n婆婆姓司徒，她事後在醫院憶述事件說：「跌咗衫出街，用支竹撩，但係唔夠長，越伸越出、越伸越出就跌咗落去。我先生捉住我隻腳(半天吊)，可能驚動隔離睇到(報警)。下次仲敢咩！我唔知會跌出去呀！好彩我踩(應為捉)住個篷(晾衫架)，如果個篷(晾衫架)殘殘哋跌咗落去喇!」<br />\n<br />\n婆婆姓關的丈夫說，今早不見了妻子，找尋下見到她竟然在廚房窗外，連忙捉住她的腳。關伯伯說：「她自己捉實晒，響出面晾衫架捉實，我發現就拉佢上嚟，但我唔夠力，鄰居就幫手報警。」他表示會考慮裝窗花，以防案件重演。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170323/large/1490231284_51c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170323%2Flarge%2F1490231284_51c6.jpg&h=13df9f1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n婆婆的丈夫指考慮安裝窗花。(江寶龍攝)"},{"pid":"6ea2e4a01780881fe1d78491cc9828e6618b2f5a","tid":167511,"uid":56439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T03:08:16.000Z","msg":"阿婆都幾fit"},{"pid":"2fbbea5ba572dda7941a53a76677860dd4fb2e54","tid":167511,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T03:10:01.000Z","msg":"痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81e7213d18b06d7eb04a9f62c6a37c873b6b8450","tid":167511,"uid":11571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T03:20:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>阿婆都幾fit</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a51ff3b60e75149d747f0f4d955771103a2468ee","tid":167511,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T03:22:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>阿婆都幾fit</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n班九十後打歪廢"},{"pid":"1d2aa857d3387f0d4ea70184fe9a4509736212c1","tid":167511,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T03:24:29.000Z","msg":"啲廢老唔注重安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}